<main class="container-medium container-solution">
  <div class="solution-page-card">
    <h1 class="title h2-size">About BWS</h1>
    <p class="paragraph" style="max-width:720px;">
      BWS (Blockchain Web Services) is a product studio built on one idea: <strong>demand becomes product</strong>. We
      turn validated market demand into production-ready software, fast — and add a blockchain dimension only when it
      meaningfully deepens the customer outcome.
    </p>

    <h2 class="title h3-size" style="margin-top:36px;">What we do</h2>
    <p class="paragraph" style="max-width:720px;">
      Instead of betting on ideas in isolation, we start from evidence of real demand and run it through a consolidated,
      AI-native build workflow. The result is a growing marketplace of focused products — from WhatsApp and calendar
      tooling to digital credentials, IPFS infrastructure, and developer tooling — each shipped to solve a specific,
      observed problem.
    </p>

    <h2 class="title h3-size" style="margin-top:36px;">How we work</h2>
    <p class="paragraph" style="max-width:720px;">
      Our workflow pairs market-demand-first selection with disciplined, AI-assisted engineering: specs before prompts,
      validation before generation, and traceability by default. Blockchain is treated as added value — used where
      verifiability, provenance, or trust genuinely improve the product, not as a default.
    </p>

    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:32px;">
